nhc_headline: ...IMELDA FORECAST TO BECOME A HURRICANE LATER TODAY...
summary: ...IMELDA FORECAST TO BECOME A HURRICANE LATER TODAY... As of 2:00 AM EDT Tue Sep 30 the center of Imelda was located near 28.5, -77.2 with movement N at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 983 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
